      <title>Amundi 有意收购安联全球投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/amundi-said-to-be-interested-in-buying-allianz-global-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，法国公司 Amundi SA 有意收购安联集团旗下资产管理公司安联全球投资者 (Allianz Global Investors) 的控制权，因为在行业整合的背景下，这家公司正在寻找交易机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/amundi-said-to-be-interested-in-buying-allianz-global-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 19:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
